# Release Process: {{PROJECT_NAME}}

## Version Scheme
[Semantic Versioning](https://semver.org/): `MAJOR.MINOR.PATCH`
- `PATCH` — bug fixes, no API changes
- `MINOR` — new features, backwards-compatible
- `MAJOR` — breaking changes

