## Release Steps (automated by `/release`)

1. Bump version in `{{VERSION_FILE}}`
2. Regenerate `{{VERSION_INJECT_FILE}}` (build-time version injection)
3. Update `CHANGELOG.md` from commits since last tag
4. Commit: `chore: release vX.Y.Z`
5. Tag: `vX.Y.Z`
6. Push branch + tag
7. GitHub Actions `release.yml` triggers and:
   - Runs tests
   - Builds
   - Publishes to {{PUBLISH_TARGET}}
   - Creates GitHub Release with CHANGELOG notes

